Connections.Comments: It’s a hotel charger but open for everyone.  JUICE BOOSTER 2 mobile wallbox can be connected in both single and three phase with a maximum charging power of 7,4kW/16A single phase ( 220 V ) and 22kW/32A three phase (440V).
